  "system": {
    "description": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to attempt to beguile a Beast that can see or hear you. Make an <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Animal </strong><strong>Check</strong> contested by the target’s <strong>Charisma</strong> <strong>Save</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Success:</strong> The animal is <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Taunted</strong> by you for 1 minute (Repeated Save) or until you target it with a harmful Attack, Spell, or other effect.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Success (5):</strong> It’s also <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Impaired</strong>. </span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Success (10):</strong> It’s also <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Charmed</strong>.</span></p>",
